					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="featured-content">
				<h2>Latest Insights</h2>
				<p>Sharing practical DevOps implementations, automation strategies, and technical deep-dives from real-world projects</p>
				<div class="content-links">
					<a href="/blog" class="content-link">üìñ Read My Blog Posts</a>
					<a href="/about" class="content-link">üë®‚Äçüíª Learn More About Me</a>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="cta-section">
				<h2>Ready to Optimize Your DevOps?</h2>
				<p>Let's discuss how we can streamline your infrastructure, automate deployments, and accelerate your DevOps transformation.</p>
				<div class="cta-buttons">
					<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/akshay-sinha-91215954/" target="_blank" class="cta-button primary">üìß Get In Touch</a>
					<a href="mailto:akshaysin@gmail.com" class="cta-button secondary">ÔøΩ Let's Talk</a>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
